{
  "chapter": 15,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述了刘挺之、叶谷浑和邓中艾三人搜捕杨华和金碧漪。刘挺之用虎啸引出马匹，发现杨华踪迹。杨华与三人激战，金碧漪突然失踪。杨华突围后遇到金逐流之子，对方误以为杨华轻薄金碧漪，与之比剑。杨华夺其长剑，结下梁子。杨华下山后在平安集客栈投宿，发现金碧漪可能也在客栈，用传音入密试探。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ting_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "刘大哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“刘大哥”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ting_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "刘大哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“刘大哥”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ting_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "刘大哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“刘大哥”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_zhong_ai",
      "speaker_name": "邓中艾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“怪不得你们宁可不要知县老爷的殷勤招待，也不在衙门里舒舒服眼睡一个觉，连夜就赶来了。但你们怎不早点告诉我呢？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ting_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "刘大哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“刘大哥”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ting_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "刘大哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我是想令你惊奇一下呀。老邓，假如当真是那两个小子，你怕不怕？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_zhong_ai",
      "speaker_name": "邓中艾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“刘大哥，你也忒小看我了，我虽然本领不济，败给那两个小贼之仇是非报不可的。何况你们两位大内高手，有你们两位撑腰，我还会害怕他们吗？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ting_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "刘大哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“刘大哥”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ting_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "刘大哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我是和你开玩笑的，你别介意。其实以你的铁笔点穴功夫，未必真的就会输给那两个小子，我猜大概是因为初次和他交手，未模得清楚他的剑法，以至在他快剑狂攻之下，冷不防就吃了亏。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_zhong_ai",
      "speaker_name": "邓中艾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“刘大哥”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_zhong_ai",
      "speaker_name": "邓中艾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“刘大哥明见，当时的情形确是如此。但愿他们真的是在这座山中。不过这座山这么大，怎知他们躲在何处？黑夜里还得提防他先发现我们，突来偷袭。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ting_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "刘大哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“刘大哥”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ting_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "刘大哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“老邓不用担心，我有办法知道他们躲藏之处。而且料想他们也想不到会有人到这荒山来搜捕他们，所以只有咱们偷袭他们，不会反而给他们偷袭的。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_zhong_ai",
      "speaker_name": "邓中艾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“刘大哥，你有甚么妙法？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ting_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "刘大哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“刘大哥”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“此人内力深厚，倒是不可小觑。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“原来刘大哥还有这样的绝妙口技，小弟却不知道。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ting_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "刘大哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“刘大哥”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_zhong_ai",
      "speaker_name": "邓中艾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“你这法子果然是妙，马在那边，人也一定是在那边。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ting_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "刘大哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“刘大哥”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_zhong_ai",
      "speaker_name": "邓中艾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“你怎么知道？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ting_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "刘大哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“刘大哥”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ting_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "刘大哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“刘大哥”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ting_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "刘大哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我怀疑这两匹战马，就是马昆和周灿的坐骑。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_hun",
      "speaker_name": "姓叶的",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“如此说来，他们二人岂非已遭毒手？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ting_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "刘大哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“刘大哥”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_zhong_ai",
      "speaker_name": "邓中艾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我们现在可以去找那两个小贼了吗？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ting_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "刘大哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“刘大哥”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ting_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "刘大哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“对，现在是他们在明处，咱们在暗处，待他松懈的时候，咱们便可以进行偷袭了。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“用不着现在就惊动金兄，谅这三个鹰爪，我还对付得了。就是对付不了，金兄不久也会跑来的。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“现在是时候了，咱们去找那个小贼吧！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“用不着你们费神寻找了，我在这儿！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_zhong_ai",
      "speaker_name": "邓中艾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“正是这个小贼！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ting_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "刘大哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“刘大哥”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ting_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "刘大哥",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“唰”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“你弄这些鬼门道，就想吓倒我么？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ting_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "刘挺之",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“刘大哥”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“织女投梭”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“织女投梭”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ting_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "刘挺之",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“刘大哥”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“开首十数招，我不求有功，但求无过，这小子剑法纵然诡异，谅也难奈我何。待摸熟他的路数，那时再下杀手不迟。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“各个击破”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_hun",
      "speaker_name": "姓叶的",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“玉带围腰”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_hun",
      "speaker_name": "姓叶的",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那姓叶的哼了一声说道：“你这小子真是大胆妄为，我本来不想以大欺小，以众凌寡。\n\n，可怪不得我了！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“八名大内高手”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ting_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "刘挺之",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“刘大哥”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_hun",
      "speaker_name": "叶谷浑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这小子的剑法又像青城，又像峨嵋，又像少林，又像武当，不知是哪一派的剑法？天下竞有这样的剑法，真是古怪！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“两位大哥，我和这小贼在小金川结有一段梁子，小弟并非想与你们争功，而是这段梁子非得报复不可！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“再多几个又有何妨，你把小金川的那些甚么五官、四道、四僧找来更好。嘿嘿，以多欺寡这已经是你们的的绝技了。上就上吧，何必还找藉口？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_zhong_ai",
      "speaker_name": "邓中艾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“好小子，死到临头，还敢猖狂！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“期门穴”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“叠翠浮青”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“叠翠浮青”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“你用似是而非的嵩山剑法扰人耳目，以为邓某还会上你的当么？嘿嘿，你也真是黔驴技穷了！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“夜叉探海”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“叠翠浮青”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“叠翠浮青”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“有备而战”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“运用之妙，存乎一心，兵法如此，剑术亦然。你给我胡乱编派是哪一派的剑法，强作解人，不是太可笑了吗？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“小子，今日不是你死，便是我亡！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“邓兄不必生气，这小子已是网底之鱼，谅他也是飞不出咱们手心的了。待会儿捉着了他，你高兴怎样处置就怎样处置他。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“放你的屁，咱们骑驴念唱本，走着瞧吧！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“要是那个使软鞭的少年当真和他一起，出来帮他，只怕我们还是难逃一败。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“虎啸”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“传音入密”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_zhong_ai",
      "speaker_name": "邓中艾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这小子要找帮手，咱们快点干掉他！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ting_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "刘挺之",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“穷小子，来不及啦！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_bi_yi",
      "speaker_name": "金碧漪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“奇怪，莫非这小子不是和他一起？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_bi_yi",
      "speaker_name": "金碧漪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我看这小子害怕咱们，顾不得朋友，自己逃命去啦！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“碧漪决不会是这样的人，那日他助我狠斗五官、四道、四僧，我和他还是未知名的陌生人呢！今晚这三个敌人本领虽高，也不见得比五官、四道、四僧联手更为难斗，碧漪又怎会害怕他们？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“难道他也和我一样，遭遇了什么意外的事情？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“叠翠浮青”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“铁门闩”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“金兄，金兄！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这人似乎不是碧漪，但他的功力却是不在碧漪之下！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“滚开”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“是”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_bi_yi",
      "speaker_name": "金碧漪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“五官”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“卜通”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“奇怪，他在害怕什么？要跑，为什么也不和我打个招呼？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“多谢兄台赶走那三个鹰爪孙……”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“你是何人？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我这样客气对他，怎的他却如此之没礼貌！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“小弟杨华，木易杨，中华的华，请问兄台高姓大名？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“哦，你叫杨华？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“杨华”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“金碧漪是不是和你一起的？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“不错。你和他也是相熟的吗？那么咱们可是自家人了。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“自家人”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“刚才他还在这里睡觉，但如今我却不知他是到哪里去了。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“你不知道，我知道，但他是不敢见我，躲起来啦。哼，好不要脸！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我不知道你是他什么人，也不知道他是否怕你而躲开的，不过，他是我的好朋友，你不能这样随便侮辱我的朋友！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我还要骂你呢，你们两人都不要脸！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我有什么不要脸了？你怎能胡乱骂人！你不说个清楚，我、我……”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“说出来污我的口，我只问你，你要怎样？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“不知他对我有什么误会，但他替我赶走那三个鹰爪，想必不是坏人。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我也不要你怎样，但你不该胡乱乱骂，你道个歉吧！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“你这个轻薄无行的小子，居然还敢要我道歉？赶快拔剑吧！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“你我素不相识，你怎么知道我是轻薄无行？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我不和你多说，赶快拔剑！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“拔剑作什？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我要教训教训你这小子！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“好端端的我为什么要和你……”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“砰”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“咱们好好比划比划！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“误会”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这人除了功力不如缪长风之外，剑法的高明，似乎还在缪长风之上。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“可惜，可惜！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“可惜什么？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“你这小子剑法倒还不错，可惜就是轻薄无行！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“轻薄无行”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“你讲不讲理了；你说说看，我到底怎样——”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“轻薄无行”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“只怕我必须把他当作敌人，方能招架得了！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“平淡”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“武学中的最高境界是返噗归真，举重若轻，以拙胜巧。此人剑术，虽然未达到炉火纯青，但走的却正是这个路子。上乘剑术的‘重、拙、大’三字，看来他是要比我领会得多。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“李广射石”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“看你还能抵挡几招？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“敌我两忘”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“以我为主，与其为客犯主，不如以主迎客”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“制造”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“天山雪崩”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“金针度劫”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“金针度劫”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“飞龙在天”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“举火撩天”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“避其朝锐，击其暮归”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“好小子，我和你不能算完，你等着瞧吧！夺剑之辱，我若不报，誓不为人。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“兄台请回，我、我向你道歉！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“连姓名都未知道，就和这人结了梁子，真是莫名其妙！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_hun",
      "speaker_name": "叶谷浑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“你们听见蹄声没有？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_zhong_ai",
      "speaker_name": "邓中艾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“前后两次，都听见了。似乎是一骑向西，一骑向东。好在不是向咱们这方向跑来。奇怪，他们怎么不走同一方向？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_hun",
      "speaker_name": "叶谷浑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这有什么奇怪，这两个小子事先没有约定，山上那小子逃走的时候，山下那小子还在和咱们拼斗呢。后来逃跑的这个小子想必以为他的朋友是回到玉树山去。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_gu_hun",
      "speaker_name": "叶谷浑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“想不到咱们白走一遍，毫无所获！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ting_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "刘挺之",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“难想得到横里杀出一个程咬金呢？还算咱们运气不错，要是让他们三个会合，咱们恐怕还要吃亏！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_zhong_ai",
      "speaker_name": "邓中艾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“后来来的那个小子，当真是金逐流的儿子么？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_zhong_ai",
      "speaker_name": "邓中艾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“那还有假？如果我不是确实知道他是金逐流的儿子，我岂能那样忍气吞声，他喝我滚我就滚呢？嘿嘿，你是不是笑我刚才胆子大过小了？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_zhong_ai",
      "speaker_name": "邓中艾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“哪里，哪里，刘大哥，你这是应付得宜。单独一个金逐流的儿子，咱们原是不用怕，但他的剑法一定比那个姓杨的小子还要高强，两个人联手，咱们已是没有便宜可占。何况咱们也得罪不起金逐流呢！好汉不吃眼前亏，当然是三十六着走为上着了！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“要是我早知道他是金逐流的儿子，我就不会和他打这一架了。如今可是糊里糊涂的和这位金少侠结上粱子啦。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“金逐流只有一个儿子，那么金碧漪当然不会也是了。不过他们同是姓金，或许是堂兄弟也说不定，故此他要来找金碧漪。但是，他为什么要骂我轻薄无行？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_si",
      "speaker_name": "小厮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“客官是来投店的么？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“不错。请问贵店的客人多不多？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_si",
      "speaker_name": "小厮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“生意清淡得很，好几天没有客人上门，今天方才来了两个。你打听这个干嘛？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我担心没有房间。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_si",
      "speaker_name": "小厮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“你要十间都有。进去吧。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这两个客人多大年纪，可是和我一样，从外地来的么？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我一向不爱多管闲事，没有问过是那里来的，年纪多大，我也不会看，有一个有胡子，有一个没胡子，大概总比我年纪长吧。你管他们的年纪做什么？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“随便问问。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他有过在小金川寻访义军的经验，见这小颗对他似乎怀有敌意，不由得心头一凛，霍然省起：“自己可能已经惹起了他的疑心，当下也就不敢多问了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“小姓杨。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_zhu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "店主人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“杨大爷，你上哪儿？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_zhu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "店主人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我是往鄂克昭盟找活干的。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_zhu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "店主人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“往鄂克昭盟为何不走平路？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“走山路快些，那边的雇主等着用人。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_zhu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "店主人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“不过山区近来不大平静，你知道么？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_zhu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "店主人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我身无长物，怕什么？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_zhu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "店主人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“好，我给你一间上房。你吃过晚饭没有？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“在集上吃过了。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_zhu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "店主人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“杨大爷，你很喜欢喝酒的吗？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_zhu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "店主人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我闻得酒香，你这皮袋里敢情是葡萄酒吧。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“不错，你真是大行家，连什么酒都闻得出来。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_zhu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "店主人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我们这个小市集似乎没有这样好的葡萄酒！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_zhu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "店主人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这是前几天在路上买的。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_zhu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "店主人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“原来如此。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“纵然他有疑心，料他也不会猜得着酒的来历。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_zhu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "店主人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“抱歉得很，小店设备简陋，连蚊帐也没有，好在现在是冬天，也没蚊子。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_zhu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "店主人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“客官请早安歇。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_bi_yi",
      "speaker_name": "金碧漪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这是天蚕丝织成的帐，这样好的宝贝却有人随手抛掉，好在我捡起来。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“恐怕是我的一厢情愿了，天下哪有这样的巧事，金碧漪也会刚好在这小客栈里？天下白马多得很，那匹白马，也未必就是他的座骑。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“天下哪有这样的巧事？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“城阙辅三秦，风烟望五津。\n\n与君离别意，同是宦游人。\n\n海内存知已，天涯若比邻。\n\n无为在歧路，儿女共沾巾。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“之任”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“城阙辅三秦”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“三秦”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“五津”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“城阙辅三秦”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“与君离别意，同是宦游人。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“你为了做官的原故，远去蜀川，我也，是为了做官来到长安，同属宦游，之身，远离乡土作客他方的感触，彼此都是一样的。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“海内存知己，天涯若比令。。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“侠义道”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“宦游人”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“海内存知己，天涯若比令！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "杨华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“海内存知己，天涯若比邻。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    }
